meta.title: UJL Framework - Brand-Compliance by Design
meta.description: You shouldn't have to choose between moving fast and protecting your brand. With UJL, you get both: launch professional websites in minutes instead of weeks, while your brand guidelines stay locked in.

content.text: You shouldn't have to choose between moving fast and protecting your brand. With UJL, you can have the best of both worlds: launch professional websites in minutes instead of weeks while keeping your brand guidelines intact. Your team can work freely while your design stays intact.

Give your clients the freedom to edit content without fearing that they will break your design. When brand rules are built into the system, mistakes simply can't happen. Say goodbye to late-night support calls about accidentally changing the brand colour.

Accessibility isn't an afterthought  it's built in from the outset. Every page you create automatically meets WCAG standards. There are no expensive audits, painful retrofitting or legal headaches. You can be sure that your content is accessible every time.

Use AI to create content without worrying about brand violations. Every layout that AI generates is automatically validated against your brand rules, enabling you to work quickly without compromising on what matters most.

fields.alt: Gentle, abstract motif in warm backlighting: a blurred figure touches a floating, glowing ball of energy surrounded by flowing bands of light and fine particles  a calm, inspiring mood of the future.

content.text: Built for teams who refuse to compromise

The campaign is launching next week. Your IT team says they need three. Sound familiar? With UJL, you can create fully brand-compliant landing pages in minutes, even when the clock is ticking. There are no compromises or shortcuts, just results.

Do you remember that sinking feeling after handing over a project? When clients start making edits and you're waiting for the first 'something broke' email? With UJL, clients can edit freely  your design is protected. Rest assured that your work will stay intact.

Stop spending months building custom editors from scratch. Integrate UJL in weeks, not months. Since it's open source, there are no licensing fees  just superior software that you have full control over.

We built UJL to have an impact. Digital accessibility happens automatically  no expertise is required. Our AI-native approach uses smaller, more efficient models that reduce energy consumption by up to 80%. Because it's open source, you have complete control over your data and infrastructure. This isn't just better software. It's better for everyone.

fields.headline: Ready to move fast without breaking your brand?

content.text: We're looking for two to three forward-thinking agencies to join our pilot programme. Test UJL with real client projects and help us to shape the future of website development. Enjoy early access, direct influence and zero risk.
